        <div n="365-79L1">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-365-79L1-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-365-79L1-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-365-79L1-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">In order to be admitted to speak to him, when he was DEAF, 1724.&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-365-79L1-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-365-79L1-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-365-79L1-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-365-79L1-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-365-79L1-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-365-79L1-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">D</hi>EAR sir, I think 'tis doubly hard,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-2" n="2">Your ears and doors should both be barr'd.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-3" n="3">Can any thing be more unkind?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-4" n="4">Must I not see, 'cause you are blind?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-5" n="5">Methinks a friend at night should cheer you,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-6" n="6">A friend that loves to see and hear you.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-7" n="7">Why am I robb'd of that delight,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-8" n="8">When you can be no loser by·'t?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-9" n="9">Nay, when 'tis plain (for what is plainer?)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-10" n="10">That, if you heard, you·'d be no gainer?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-11" n="11">For sure you are not yet to learn,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-12" n="12">That hearing is not your concern.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-13" n="13">Then be your doors no longer barr'd:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-79L1-line-14" n="14">Your business, sir, is to be heard.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
